&lt;p&gt;Hartlepool &amp; Stockton Health Ltd are recruiting on behalf of the Seaton Surgery&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Part time Advanced Nurse Practitioner&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting and challenging opportunity has arisen for an Advanced Nurse Practitioner to join our friendly practice team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated and enthusiastic team player who can demonstrate high standards of clinical excellence.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience working in a General Practice environment would be an advantage but is not essential, the successful applicant will hold an MSc or Bsc Advanced Nurse Practitioner / Advanced Practice qualification and also hold the Independent non-medical prescribing qualification. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be experienced, dynamic and committed to providing high standards of care.  You will demonstrate safe clinical decision making working collaboratively with the General Practice team to meet the needs of our patients. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3500 patients (approx.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SystmOne computer system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High QOF achievement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Friendly, experienced practice team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Special interest &amp; personal development supported&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CQC rated as Good in all&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent salary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6 weeks holiday (pro rata) &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
